    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings housing institutions that are typically more like museums or archives than libraries, containing the papers and sometimes exhibits about a given U.S. president and his administration. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
